-- ANALYSTS VIEW: Lawmakers agree on bailout blueprint
-- 
-- Sun Sep 28, 2008 5:13pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/28/us-usa-economy-bailout-idUSTRE48R38T20080928

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - U.S. Congressional leaders agreed on Sunday to the underpinnings of a deal that will allow the Treasury Department to buy up to $700 billion in troubled securities to soothe global credit markets. 

